19
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:29,032
The pain we feel is a lesson we learn

20
00:01:29,033 --> 00:01:30,781
Once we're broken

21
00:01:30,782 --> 00:01:33,786
but we're still playing games with our hearts

22
